methods.name: withdrawExcessAssets
methods.desc:
If someone deposits excess assets to this smart contract biatec can use them.


Only addressExecutiveFee is allowed to execute this method.

args.name: appBiatecConfigProvider
args.desc: Biatec config app. Only addressExecutiveFee is allowed to execute this method.

args.desc: Asset to withdraw. If native token, then zero

args.name: amount
args.desc: Amount of the asset to be withdrawn
